---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="HIPAA Compliance - VoiceROI"
  description="Learn about VoiceROI's HIPAA compliance measures and how we protect healthcare information in our AI digital worker solutions."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-20">
    <section class="section-padding bg-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">HIPAA Compliance</h1>
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Last updated: January 2025</p>
            
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Commitment to Healthcare Privacy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
              VoiceROI is committed to maintaining the highest standards of data protection and privacy, especially when serving healthcare organizations. We understand the critical importance of protecting Protected Health Information (PHI) and maintaining HIPAA compliance.
            </p>
            
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">HIPAA Safeguards</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
              <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Administrative Safeguards</h3>
                <p class="text-blue-700">Comprehensive policies, procedures, and training programs to ensure proper handling of PHI by all team members.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-4">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-800 mb-2">Physical Safeguards</h3>
                <p class="text-green-700">Secure data centers, controlled access to systems, and proper disposal of PHI-containing materials.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-500 p-4">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-purple-800 mb-2">Technical Safeguards</h3>
                <p class="text-purple-700">Encryption, access controls, audit logs, and secure transmission protocols for all PHI.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Business Associate Agreements</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
              For healthcare clients, VoiceROI enters into Business Associate Agreements (BAAs) that clearly define our responsibilities in handling PHI and ensure compliance with all HIPAA requirements.
            </p>
            
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Data Security Measures</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
              <li>End-to-end encryption for all data transmission</li>
              <li>Secure, HIPAA-compliant cloud infrastructure</li>
              <li>Regular security audits and vulnerability assessments</li>
              <li>Multi-factor authentication for system access</li>
              <li>Comprehensive audit trails and monitoring</li>
              <li>Secure data backup and disaster recovery procedures</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Healthcare Industry Experience</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
              Our team has extensive experience working with healthcare organizations, understanding the unique challenges and requirements of the healthcare industry while maintaining the highest standards of patient privacy and data security.
            </p>
            
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Contact Us About HIPAA Compliance</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
              If you're a healthcare organization interested in our services or have questions about our HIPAA compliance measures, please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>VoiceROI HIPAA Compliance Team</strong><br>
                Email: Hello@voiceroi.com<br>
                Phone: 646-651-4547<br>
                <em>Request a BAA and compliance documentation</em>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>